<div class="mx-auto container text-center justify-content-center align-items-center" id="container">
	<h1>Student Organization Marketplace</h1>
	<p>Support your favorite on campus organizations with the click of a button!
	<br> Search for products, organizations, & more! <br> Track sales for your organization!
	</p>
	<button class="container text-center">Read More</button>
